{"tid":1511341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急!!!!】要大大聲話俾美國知道我地需要一個攬炒的《香港人權及民主法案》","createTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T16:14:08.000Z","uid":100697,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c3bacb85ef199edf23735dca9ccbdbed7436db16","tid":1511341,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">各位手足<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都好清楚，有4位泛民議員同葉劉去美國游說美國不要「經濟制裁香港」，公民黨亦已在FB澄清「絕無此共識」。<br />\n<br />\n即使如此，我依然強烈建議大家要大大聲話俾美國國會的議員知道，香港人需要的，不只是凍結中國官員資產的跛腳鴨法案，而是有經濟制裁香港，取消香港「獨立關稅區」地位的《香港人權及民主法案》！！！香港係中國的生門，無左「獨立關稅區」地位中共等於自廢武功，我們才有可能讓中國放生香港，實踐自治權！</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">或者大家可能覺得既然公民黨澄清了絕無此事，只是葉劉單方面游說美國「不要經濟制裁香港」，決不能改變美國國會議員的投票意願，因此認為這樣做是多此一舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我淨係想講，未來兩星期係法案通過的關鍵時刻。如果泛民係會上真係游說過美國國會唔要經濟制裁呢？破壞力係好大。佢地係民主派的代表，美國議員係好可能會以為依個係香港抗爭者的「共識」而不選擇制裁香港，通過一個跛腳鴨的法案，我們過去兩個月手足的血、受過的凌辱全全部部付諸流水。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我真心唔知道泛民有無出賣過我地，但我淨係想講，依個法案係好多手足用血，係用血換返黎，我絕絕對對唔會用佢地條命去博「無」依個可能性。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n當我地係度爭拗緊泛民的忠誠時，時間已經所剩無幾了。9月9日之前，我不想花時間玩分化說誰誰誰賣港務，不想無聊地追擊泛民議員，而是希望盡我最大的努力，游說美國國會議員，讓他們了解香港人的真正意願。你呢</span> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地可以做的事：<br />\n<br />\n1. 係民間記者會說明香港人需要的是點樣的《香港人權及民主法案》<br />\n<br />\n2. Twitter, Facebook 用盡一切方法接觸美國兩黨的國會議員，說明香港人的意願<br />\n<br />\n3. 寫信俾美國國會議員</span></span>"},{"pid":"aacdc3a4a4361f8e150a9b743b3ea569d67c9802","tid":1511341,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"30912d9eb82d47483f8b335aa2ac064bf84ec281","tid":1511341,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85cf1285966cedaef102f53cd1533be267c2ea8a","tid":1511341,"uid":295349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:24:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n生死存亡呀依家 大家唔好鬆懈!!!!"},{"pid":"1780a4c8a299ee7c6131ef8122f8f88632528ceb","tid":1511341,"uid":195573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"af84863e336c49b5f93491f402247eda7645aed8","tid":1511341,"uid":294765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2249ef9a3bcce7ae004b0c17cf182ce06510c91e","tid":1511341,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 不要支籍<br />\n&ldquo;中國單方面宣稱中英聯合聲明已經失效，香港人該何去何從？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n用1分鐘嘅時間簽名，務求收集到10萬簽名將BNO平權議題推上議會討論<br />\n註: 轉BC後可傳俾97後<br />\n為咗你自己，仲有你嘅摯愛，簽名？刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\nPostal Code 請填000000，如果身處英國就填所在地點嘅Code<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxtagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=e20ced40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"1286222de49a53ae266ee1370df4d1d3b1b364d1","tid":1511341,"uid":70363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}